at_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany landed in ninth and seventh in men's and sixth and first in women's team pursuit and sprint, respectively.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.833437810867383, \"rank\": 0.1997476446934379, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team sizes confirmed for Paris 2024 Olympics road race and time trialOlympics: Mads Pedersen, Skjelmose, M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v selected to Danish team for ParisLaura Kenny retires from cycling ahead of Paris 2024 Olympics  Canada ended the team pursuit 2022-2024 rankings in eighth place to secure maximum team size for the men's endurance races, narrowly edging Poland out of the top eight and eighth in the team pursuit rankings.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.082424772125618e-18, \"text\": \"road race\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9973584045699821, \"ran