289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v has already been named to Denmark's team to play dual roles in the road race to support Mads Pedersen and to compete in the Madison.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v\", \"score\": 0.9999973201406175, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_M\\u00f8rk\\u00f8v\"}, {\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.7852267604358718, \"rank\": 0.2438507876877644, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}, {\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9973584045699821, \"rank\": 0.0026481297583587347, \"text\": \"Mads Pedersen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 2429, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"score\": 0.8269773544220516, \"rank\": 0.2092229547188776, \"text\": \"Madison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qualification for the track cycling events hinges on the team events, with the top 10 countries in the team pursuit and the top 8 in the team sprint UCI Olympic rankings automatically making the cut.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.852126043001534e-15, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nations that qualified in the Team Sprint can enter two athletes into the Sprint and Keirin using athletes already qualified in another track event or cycling discipline.\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2670, \"end\": 2681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.642048695150415e-33, \"text\": \"Team Sprint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\"}, {\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.947214913003065, \"rank\": 0.05104204604015747, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1269399234266253e-56, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nations that made the Team Pursuit cut can also field a Madison team and one spot for the Omnium under the same conditions.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9531614198575617e-37, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}, {\"begin\": 